name: To the Moon (Dogecoin Version)
description: This is a proof-of-concept work that attempts to utilize NFTs as "proof-of-ownership" that extends into the "real world" as well. The NFT here acts as proof of validation for the physical artwork itself, which will be shipped to the buyer separately as a package. (Contact separately for more details. This work also comes with a certificate of authenticity of the submerged Dogecoin from 2014.)
